			<id>http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/156</id>
			<title>The Annual Tax on Enveloped Dwellings (Indexation of Annual Chargeable Amounts) Order 2026</title>
			<link rel="self" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/156"/>
			<link href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made"/>
			<link rel="alternate" type="application/xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.xml" title="XML"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/rdf+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.rdf" title="RDF/XML"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/akn+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.akn" title="AKN"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/xhtml+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.xht" title="HTML snippet"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/akn+xhtml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.html" title="HTML5"/><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.htm" title="Website (XHTML) Default View"/><link rel="alternate" type="text/csv" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.csv" title="CSV"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/pdf" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/made/data.pdf" title="PDF"/>
			<link rel="http://purl.org/dc/terms/tableOfContents" type="application/xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2026/156/contents/made" title="Table of Contents"/>
			<author><name/></author>
			<updated>2026-02-24T13:56:15Z</updated>
			<published>2026-02-24T13:25:41.773907Z</published>
			<ukm:DocumentMainType Value="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument"/><ukm:Year Value="2026"/><ukm:Number Value="156"/><ukm:ISBN Value="9780348279740"/><ukm:CreationDate Date="2026-02-24"/><ukm:Subject Value="ANNUAL TAX ON ENVELOPED DWELLINGS"/>
			
			
			<category term="ANNUAL TAX ON ENVELOPED DWELLINGS"/>
			<summary>This Order fulfils the indexation requirements in section 101 (indexation of annual chargeable amounts) of the Finance Act 2013 (c. 29) in respect of the annual chargeable amounts which are increased by reference to the consumer price index (CPI). The annual chargeable amounts for the annual tax on enveloped dwellings are set out in section 99 (amount of tax chargeable) of that Act.</summary>
		</entry><entry>
