			<ukm:DocumentMainType Value="UnitedKingdomStatutoryInstrument"/><ukm:Year Value="2026"/><ukm:Number Value="152"/><ukm:ISBN Value="9780348279702"/><ukm:CreationDate Date="2026-02-23"/><ukm:Subject Value="RATING AND VALUATION, ENGLAND"/>
			<ukm:Supersedes URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ukdsi/2026/9780348278132"><dc:title xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">The Local Government Finance Act 1988 (Prescription of Non-Domestic Rating Multipliers) (England) Regulations 2026</dc:title><ukm:DocumentMainType Value="UnitedKingdomDraftStatutoryInstrument"/><ukm:Year Value="2026"/><ukm:ISBN Value="9780348278132"/></ukm:Supersedes>
			
			<category term="RATING AND VALUATION, ENGLAND"/>
			<summary>In relation to England, a ratepayer’s liability to a non-domestic rate as regards a hereditament is determined in accordance with the Local Government Finance Act 1988 (c. 41). Liability as regards occupied local rating properties, unoccupied local rating properties and central rating is determined in accordance with formulae in Schedules 4ZA, 4ZB and 5A to that Act.</summary>
		</entry><entry>
			<id>http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/107</id>
			<title>The Criminal Legal Aid and Assistance by Way of Representation (Miscellaneous Amendment) (Scotland) Regulations 2026</title>
			<link rel="self" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/ssi/2026/107"/>
			<link href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made"/>
			<link rel="alternate" type="application/xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.xml" title="XML"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/rdf+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.rdf" title="RDF/XML"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/akn+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.akn" title="AKN"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/xhtml+xml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.xht" title="HTML snippet"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/akn+xhtml" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.html" title="HTML5"/><link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.htm" title="Website (XHTML) Default View"/><link rel="alternate" type="text/csv" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.csv" title="CSV"/><link rel="alternate" type="application/pdf" href="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2026/107/made/data.pdf" title="PDF"/>
