			<category term="ENERGY"/>
			<summary>These Regulations amend the Energy Bill Relief Scheme (Northern Ireland) Regulations 2022 (S.I. 2022/1106 NI) (the “EBRS NI Regulations”) and the Energy Bills Discount Scheme (Northern Ireland) Regulations 2023 (S.I. 2023/454 NI) (the “EBDS NI Regulations”).  The amendments achieve the same effects in relation to both Regulations.</summary>
		</entry><entry>
			<id>http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/nisr/2026/22</id>
