			<updated>2026-02-23T03:10:01Z</updated>
			<published>2026-02-23T03:04:59.704669Z</published>
			<ukm:DocumentMainType Value="NorthernIrelandStatutoryRule"/><ukm:Year Value="2026"/><ukm:Number Value="19"/><ukm:ISBN Value="9780338025807"/><ukm:CreationDate Date="2026-02-19"/><ukm:Subject Value="RATES"/>
			
			
			<category term="RATES"/>
			<summary>This Order fixes the amount of the regional rates for the year ending 31st March 2027. It fixes 30.79 pence in the pound as the amount of the regional rate to be levied on the rateable net annual values of hereditaments (“non-domestic regional rate”) and 0.5559 pence in the pound as the amount of the regional rate to be levied on the rateable capital values of hereditaments (“domestic regional rate”).</summary>
		</entry><entry>
